text: Joann Burke (born 3 November 1969) is a road cyclist from New Zealand. She was born in Otahuhu. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports- reference.com Category:New Zealand female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of New Zealand Category:Living people Category:People from Auckland Category:1969 births
